sentences.english: Anyone who beats the record will win a season pass for four people for 2007 with VIP queue-jumping status.
sentences.chinese: 破紀錄者將能取得2007年四人份優先玩貴賓季卡。

sentences.english: The participants of the VIP card membership must fill in the following information. (If applicant requires a VIP card, please also fill in the below section).
sentences.chinese: 專匯醫療貴賓卡會籍參加者必須填妥以下資料。

sentences.english: Their first subject was the diminution of the Rosings party.
sentences.chinese: 他們一開頭就談到羅新斯貴賓離開的問題。

sentences.english: This is a VIP room, it's cheaper than the deluxe room.
sentences.chinese: 這是一間貴賓房，比豪華房便宜一些。

sentences.english: The VIP is shown on the scoreboard, for your team only.
sentences.chinese: 是的貴賓的記分牌上顯示，您的團隊只。

sentences.english: Guests can also free use the brandnew hot spring baths with a appointment.
sentences.chinese: 住宿貴賓可不限次數預約無償使用全新私人風呂湯屋。

sentences.english: Michael wakes up in a guest room of The Company.
sentences.chinese: 邁可在一間“公司”的貴賓房裏醒來了。

sentences.english: From booking to paying, everybody here is a friend and a VIP.
sentences.chinese: 從預訂到付款，每個來到這兒的客人都是朋友和貴賓。

sentences.english: There are 3 Rome Leonardo Da Vinci Airport lounges (Rome Fiumicino Airport lounges) within our program.
sentences.chinese: 我們在羅馬機場有3間機場貴賓室。

sentences.english: In Standard Poodles , for example, size is getting out of control.
sentences.chinese: 比方說，在標準貴賓犬中，大小的問題已經趨於失控。

sentences.english: Would your Standard Poodle be indoor or outdoor?
sentences.chinese: 你希望把標準貴賓犬養在室內還是室外？

sentences.english: The hundred years old company welcomed visitants on that day.
sentences.chinese: 百年老字號，在這天迎來了貴賓。

sentences.english: He is the special guest on a gala occasion.
We were guests of honor of the vice mayor.We were put in a nice hotel.
sentences.chinese: 我們是副市長的貴賓，被安置於一間很好的酒店。

sentences.english: I have three poodles and a cat.
sentences.chinese: 我有三隻貴賓犬和一隻貓。

sentences.english: To go from a standard poodle to a toy, it's fairly easily done.
sentences.chinese: 從一個標準的貴賓犬到玩物，這很容易做到。
